metadata.name: The Last Supper
metadata.description:
The divine animates even that which is set in stone.

A  camera and a hand-held light source used during the night time shooting. The creation of the digital image painted manually as the camera was recording the movement of the light handled by the photographer. 

Print size available 21" x 13" // Rhyolite, Nevada, 2017


What happens after the sale? 
Here are the extras:

*** The NFT owner will receive a physical copy of the Last Supper piece.

*** 10% of the sale will be donated to UNICEF: Children Are Bearing Brunt of Intensifying Crisis in Ukraine, under the name of the owner. The receipt of the donation will be sent for proof by email.
